WEBVTT

00:12.330 --> 00:16.430
[2010]

00:17.070 --> 00:18.280
Look at this.

00:18.280 --> 00:20.480
The office has been turned upside down.

00:32.790 --> 00:33.770
What is he looking for?

00:33.770 --> 00:35.390
Director Wang, he is looking for
the pocket watch.

00:35.390 --> 00:37.190
He's been searching for a while.

00:50.880 --> 00:51.920
Prof.

00:52.380 --> 00:55.980
I thought it was for me,
since it was together with the documents.

00:58.160 --> 01:00.490
I think you should just install a tracker.

01:00.790 --> 01:01.790
If you really can't find it,

01:01.790 --> 01:03.450
I think you'll lose your mind.

01:06.030 --> 01:07.090
That's a good idea.

01:08.150 --> 01:09.880
I'll go install one after work.

02:38.780 --> 02:44.420
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

02:44.810 --> 02:47.130
[Episode 10]

02:49.710 --> 02:52.770
The perpetrator wasn't satisfied
with their dresses.

02:55.680 --> 02:57.590
If you look closely at the three dresses,

02:57.590 --> 02:59.720
you'll find they've all been altered.

03:00.710 --> 03:01.660
The red ribbons

03:02.120 --> 03:04.100
have slight fraying on the edges.

03:04.710 --> 03:06.030
They were cut from

03:06.030 --> 03:07.430
the dresses at the scene.

03:07.860 --> 03:08.630
The cuts

03:08.720 --> 03:09.920
are smooth and clean.

03:10.400 --> 03:11.800
If you don't look closely,

03:11.800 --> 03:12.800
you might miss it.

03:13.470 --> 03:14.590
Silk fabric

03:14.960 --> 03:16.020
is soft and smooth,

03:16.470 --> 03:17.930
making it hard to control.

03:18.060 --> 03:18.990
The perpetrator

03:19.430 --> 03:20.760
is skilled at tailoring

03:20.960 --> 03:22.490
and likely excels at design

03:22.690 --> 03:23.460
and sewing.

03:36.910 --> 03:38.400
This dress of Zhao Xiaoyu's,

03:38.400 --> 03:40.190
after lowering the neckline,

03:40.470 --> 03:41.670
looks more alluring,

03:41.750 --> 03:43.880
and can better accentuate her figure.

03:44.240 --> 03:45.370
It looks beautiful,

03:45.610 --> 03:46.740
but it's revealing.

03:49.240 --> 03:50.190
For the other two victims,

03:50.190 --> 03:52.150
I haven't seen videos of them
while they were alive,

03:52.150 --> 03:54.400
only photos of their red dresses
from the physical evidence.

03:54.400 --> 03:55.470
But I presume

03:55.910 --> 03:57.370
the situation is similar.

03:59.960 --> 04:01.030
Different dresses

04:01.520 --> 04:03.350
would be altered in different ways.

04:03.350 --> 04:05.150
But what they have in common is that

04:05.150 --> 04:06.590
they all have a stronger sense of design

04:06.590 --> 04:07.920
and are more revealing.

04:08.970 --> 04:10.700
You can compare them and check.

04:21.360 --> 04:23.000
That's all for today's analysis meeting.

04:23.000 --> 04:23.750
Thank you for your time, everyone.

04:23.750 --> 04:24.410
Dismissed.

04:27.800 --> 04:28.240
Mr. Wang,

04:28.240 --> 04:29.580
today's meeting was very fruitful.

04:29.580 --> 04:30.310
Captain Tan,

04:30.830 --> 04:33.270
we'd like to visit the scene again
before heading back.

04:33.270 --> 04:33.800
Yes, sir.

04:33.920 --> 04:35.270
Then I'll arrange a car for you.

04:35.270 --> 04:35.760
Okay.

04:35.920 --> 04:36.450
Zhou Jin.

04:37.310 --> 04:38.640
Zhou doesn't need to go.

04:38.680 --> 04:39.710
I'll go with them.

04:40.159 --> 04:40.920
Prof,

04:41.270 --> 04:42.270
Let us go with you.

04:42.830 --> 04:43.290
No need.

04:43.680 --> 04:44.680
I'll go with them.

04:45.120 --> 04:45.920
Zhou,

04:46.920 --> 04:49.580
you should take better care of
Professor Jiang.

04:49.750 --> 04:52.080
Look how much weight he has lost recently.

04:52.310 --> 04:54.040
Get him some delicious food.

04:57.480 --> 04:58.810
They're a young couple.

05:02.190 --> 05:03.750
You're such a lucky girl.

05:04.240 --> 05:07.000
Professor Jiang is a real treasure.

05:08.030 --> 05:09.360
Let me walk you out.

05:09.360 --> 05:09.870
Please.

05:11.270 --> 05:13.000
This isn't a grand meeting room,

05:13.000 --> 05:14.240
nor is it a bureau-wide meeting.

05:14.240 --> 05:16.020
Why did you slam the table so hard?

05:16.020 --> 05:18.040
-Sir, I was just emotional.
-Let’s go.

05:18.040 --> 05:19.370
I'll treat you to a meal.

05:20.190 --> 05:20.990
You treasure.

05:26.800 --> 05:28.680
Why are you the only one here today?

05:28.680 --> 05:31.210
The boss and his wife both went out
to restock.

05:31.630 --> 05:32.470
Where's Juan?

05:35.430 --> 05:36.960
I don't know where she went.

05:38.870 --> 05:40.120
Also two bowls of rice, please.

05:40.120 --> 05:40.630
Okay.

05:40.830 --> 05:41.600
Please excuse me.

05:41.600 --> 05:42.120
Okay.

05:45.800 --> 05:46.800
Altering dresses

05:47.390 --> 05:48.740
is probably the most unnecessary

05:48.740 --> 05:50.940
yet distinctive thing this person did.

05:51.270 --> 05:52.120
But

05:52.620 --> 05:54.820
why is he so particular about the dress?

05:56.120 --> 05:56.930
He has demands

06:00.600 --> 06:02.000
not just for the clothes,

06:02.270 --> 06:03.600
but also for the person.

06:04.480 --> 06:06.390
Clothes are the externalization
of a person's personality.

06:06.390 --> 06:07.850
Shaping a person's attire

06:08.020 --> 06:09.820
is shaping the person themself.

06:10.090 --> 06:11.570
Turning randomly selected targets

06:11.570 --> 06:12.690
into similar looks

06:13.560 --> 06:15.040
shows that whether it's the clothes,

06:15.040 --> 06:15.790
the person,

06:16.480 --> 06:17.800
or the final scene,

06:18.360 --> 06:19.430
he has a

06:19.430 --> 06:21.560
template in his mind to match against.

06:22.430 --> 06:24.750
So he might have seen the scene in 1997.

06:28.920 --> 06:30.310
Fish-Flavored Shredded Pork is ready.

06:30.310 --> 06:30.870
Coming.

06:35.480 --> 06:36.800
Where did you go just now?

06:36.800 --> 06:37.659
I had diarrhea.

06:37.720 --> 06:39.320
Hurry up, it's busy outside.

06:39.480 --> 06:42.210
Scallion Oil Chicken,
Spicy Boiled Pork Slices.

06:42.560 --> 06:43.070
Juan,

06:43.070 --> 06:44.330
you took the wrong one.

06:44.430 --> 06:45.210
This one.

06:45.750 --> 06:46.310
Hold it.

06:46.330 --> 06:47.590
Table 3, don't forget.

07:08.750 --> 07:09.720
Officer Zhou,

07:10.430 --> 07:11.890
I was just looking for you.

07:12.630 --> 07:13.960
Need me to order for you?

07:14.000 --> 07:15.330
We've already ordered.

07:19.390 --> 07:20.190
Caught a cold?

07:22.840 --> 07:24.270
A lot of people are catching colds lately.

07:24.270 --> 07:26.340
The AC in your restaurant
really is a bit too high.

07:26.340 --> 07:27.300
Be careful.

07:29.310 --> 07:30.710
Sis, you go ahead and eat.

07:30.830 --> 07:32.150
I'll go back to work.

08:05.180 --> 08:06.580
How have you been lately?

08:09.160 --> 08:10.190
I've really quit.

08:19.360 --> 08:20.620
Excuse me for a second.

08:35.030 --> 08:36.320
Give it to me!

08:36.320 --> 08:36.909
Get up!

08:37.030 --> 08:37.570
Give it to me!

08:37.570 --> 08:38.140
Get up.

08:38.320 --> 08:39.520
You told Officer Zhou

08:39.659 --> 08:40.659
that you had quit.

08:45.840 --> 08:47.640
I can't let Officer Zhou know it.

08:48.220 --> 08:50.020
I can't let Officer Zhou know it.

08:52.270 --> 08:52.940
Juan.

08:53.270 --> 08:53.960
Juan.

08:54.540 --> 08:55.400
Never stopped?

08:57.510 --> 08:58.840
I can't take it anymore.

08:58.960 --> 08:59.960
Give me a little.

08:59.960 --> 09:00.670
Give me a little.

09:00.670 --> 09:01.030
No.

09:01.320 --> 09:02.360
I can't take it anymore.

09:02.360 --> 09:02.960
Juan.

09:02.980 --> 09:03.910
Give me a little.

09:04.240 --> 09:05.080
Listen to me.

09:05.390 --> 09:06.360
Calm down.

09:15.080 --> 09:15.670
Juan,

09:15.670 --> 09:16.440
listen to me,

09:16.790 --> 09:17.440
you can make it.

09:17.440 --> 09:18.320
I know it's hard,

09:18.320 --> 09:19.140
but I can help you.

09:19.140 --> 09:19.870
Give it to me.

09:20.150 --> 09:21.200
Give it to me.

09:21.710 --> 09:22.400
Juan.

09:22.840 --> 09:24.360
Juan, is that you? Open the door.

09:24.360 --> 09:25.030
Juan.

09:26.330 --> 09:27.460
Juan, open the door.

09:27.510 --> 09:28.320
Don't go over there.

09:28.320 --> 09:29.080
Don't go.

09:29.270 --> 09:29.960
Help me.

09:30.040 --> 09:30.710
Help me.

09:30.730 --> 09:31.510
Help me.

09:31.720 --> 09:32.630
I'll help you.

09:32.630 --> 09:34.000
I don't want my parents to know it.

09:34.000 --> 09:34.840
Help me. Help me.

09:34.840 --> 09:35.770
Jiang Hansheng.

09:36.000 --> 09:37.730
Jiang Hansheng, open the door.

09:39.720 --> 09:40.450
Give it to me.

09:40.600 --> 09:41.440
Juan, what's wrong?

09:41.440 --> 09:41.960
Tell me!

09:41.960 --> 09:43.000
Did he bully you?

09:43.020 --> 09:44.080
He tried to rape me.

09:44.120 --> 09:44.980
He tried to rape me.

09:44.980 --> 09:45.510
He tried to rape you?

09:45.510 --> 09:46.840
I'll call the police right now.

09:46.840 --> 09:48.900
I am a police officer. I'll handle it.

09:49.030 --> 09:49.960
Everyone, calm down.

09:49.960 --> 09:51.000
She really is a police officer.

09:51.000 --> 09:52.200
Step back, step back.

09:52.820 --> 09:53.750
We can trust her.

09:55.440 --> 09:56.150
He tried to rape me.

09:56.150 --> 09:56.680
Zhou Jin.

10:00.320 --> 10:01.380
He tried to rape me.

10:01.480 --> 10:03.340
He tried to rape me, Officer Zhou.

10:06.790 --> 10:07.850
He tried to rape me.

10:07.910 --> 10:09.510
He's not that kind of person.

10:09.600 --> 10:10.440
He tried to rape me.

10:10.440 --> 10:11.270
Are you using again?

10:11.270 --> 10:12.150
Are you?

10:15.800 --> 10:17.230
I can't quit.

10:31.790 --> 10:33.390
These are your illegal substances.

10:33.390 --> 10:34.320
Any objections?

10:35.750 --> 10:36.320
No.

10:37.150 --> 10:38.410
Where did you get them?

10:40.270 --> 10:41.360
From a friend.

10:42.480 --> 10:43.840
What's the friend's name?

10:43.840 --> 10:44.700
What do they do?

10:46.000 --> 10:47.510
His nickname is Heipi.

10:48.390 --> 10:49.720
He's a truck driver.

10:51.600 --> 10:53.260
Please don't tell my parents.

10:54.480 --> 10:55.360
I beg you.

10:56.200 --> 10:57.750
We've already contacted them.

10:57.750 --> 10:58.630
Actually,

10:58.910 --> 11:00.710
you need your parents' help too.

11:19.720 --> 11:20.650
Blood test done?

11:23.240 --> 11:25.050
Good thing the bite didn't break the skin.

11:25.050 --> 11:25.750
It's fine.

11:38.710 --> 11:39.370
Put this on.

11:59.260 --> 12:00.600
We're done with the questions.

12:00.600 --> 12:01.510
We'll head back first.

12:01.510 --> 12:03.110
We'll contact you if needed.

12:03.320 --> 12:03.960
Okay.

12:13.720 --> 12:14.850
You're not going in?

12:15.630 --> 12:16.670
I'm still mad.

12:16.840 --> 12:17.770
I'm not going in.

12:19.670 --> 12:20.320
I'll go.

12:41.510 --> 12:42.320
We're even.

12:44.390 --> 12:45.590
I know that deep down,

12:46.170 --> 12:47.330
you want to quit.

12:47.910 --> 12:48.630
You know?

12:50.870 --> 12:52.320
You don't know anything.

12:53.050 --> 12:54.310
Other than saying some

12:54.310 --> 12:55.670
empty nice words,

12:56.360 --> 12:58.220
can you really do anything for me?

12:59.550 --> 13:00.550
Do you know...

13:01.080 --> 13:02.880
do you know what that feels like?

13:03.550 --> 13:05.670
Do you know how hard it is to quit?

13:07.750 --> 13:09.210
Sometimes I just feel like

13:10.840 --> 13:12.440
I'd be better off dead.

13:13.750 --> 13:14.440
Juan.

13:16.320 --> 13:17.120
I know.

13:27.910 --> 13:29.240
This is my contact info.

13:30.360 --> 13:31.440
If you need help,

13:32.000 --> 13:33.000
call me anytime.

13:34.550 --> 13:35.610
I have experience.

13:36.240 --> 13:37.700
I am qualified to help you.

13:41.960 --> 13:42.630
You...

13:43.270 --> 13:43.910
You too?

13:45.670 --> 13:46.440
Trust me.

13:47.320 --> 13:48.380
It will get better.

13:55.390 --> 13:56.920
How did you make it through?

14:01.830 --> 14:03.830
I had someone I really wanted to see.

14:04.240 --> 14:05.230
I hoped that one day,

14:05.230 --> 14:07.090
I could walk to her in good health.

14:10.790 --> 14:12.510
Is that person Officer Zhou?

14:23.200 --> 14:24.600
Focus on your treatment.

14:26.660 --> 14:27.660
Professor Jiang,

14:30.510 --> 14:31.200
can you

14:32.810 --> 14:34.060
give me a hug?

14:36.550 --> 14:37.280
I am married.

14:39.790 --> 14:41.390
A woman

14:42.120 --> 14:44.450
only realizes how important you are to her

14:44.790 --> 14:46.850
when she is jealous.

14:47.960 --> 14:48.560
Thank you.

14:49.670 --> 14:51.470
I don't want her to feel that way.

14:52.560 --> 14:53.620
Get some good rest.

15:03.840 --> 15:04.640
Let's go back.

15:06.940 --> 15:08.200
Is she feeling better?

15:09.320 --> 15:10.320
She's doing okay.

15:11.630 --> 15:12.790
What did you say to her?

15:12.790 --> 15:14.790
She seems to be in a much better mood.

15:16.200 --> 15:17.460
I said I would help her.

15:18.600 --> 15:20.860
Quitting drugs is a repetitive process.

15:21.240 --> 15:23.170
I hope she truly understands that.

15:25.840 --> 15:27.500
Did she try to hug you just now?

15:29.120 --> 15:29.720
No.

15:32.600 --> 15:33.550
I saw it.

16:07.990 --> 16:08.510
Heipi.

16:10.240 --> 16:11.070
Who are you?

16:12.720 --> 16:13.550
Who are you?

16:13.630 --> 16:14.290
Kneel down!

16:21.600 --> 16:22.660
Do you know who I am?

16:24.960 --> 16:26.000
You wanna die?

16:26.770 --> 16:28.300
Don't you recognize Cheng?

16:29.080 --> 16:30.240
Cheng?

16:31.080 --> 16:32.240
Ah, Cheng!

16:34.360 --> 16:36.360
I haven't had the chance
to meet you before.

16:36.360 --> 16:38.320
But of course I've heard your name.

16:38.790 --> 16:39.510
Hello, Cheng.

16:39.510 --> 16:40.310
Hello, Cheng.

16:41.240 --> 16:43.440
I heard that you've moved product
recently.

16:43.440 --> 16:44.000
I...

16:45.000 --> 16:45.720
I moved...

16:47.120 --> 16:48.050
I moved product.

16:48.360 --> 16:49.000
Yes, I did.

16:49.960 --> 16:51.290
Didn't I tell you before

16:51.480 --> 16:53.340
not to move any product recently?

16:53.390 --> 16:54.750
Why didn't you listen?

16:55.630 --> 16:56.600
I didn't know.

16:57.030 --> 16:57.440
No,

16:57.510 --> 16:58.460
it was...

16:58.790 --> 17:00.320
Minglei asked me to sell it.

17:00.320 --> 17:01.050
Nonsense!

17:03.940 --> 17:05.470
When did I ask you to sell it?

17:06.930 --> 17:08.170
Did I tell you to?

17:11.920 --> 17:12.490
Enough.

17:12.640 --> 17:14.500
Stop acting like you're wronged.

17:15.960 --> 17:18.020
You said it had nothing to do with you,

17:18.510 --> 17:20.240
and he said it had nothing to do with him.

17:20.240 --> 17:22.640
Aren't you making things difficult for me?

17:23.720 --> 17:24.750
Here's what we'll do.

17:24.750 --> 17:26.210
I'll leave your man to you.

17:26.400 --> 17:27.880
If you want to argue,
argue amongst yourselves.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.890
Just give me an explanation in the end.

17:29.890 --> 17:31.150
I only have one demand.

17:33.480 --> 17:34.920
From now on,

17:35.160 --> 17:36.640
my rules are the rules.

17:37.000 --> 17:38.270
No one can mess up my business,

17:38.270 --> 17:39.240
and no one

17:39.680 --> 17:41.400
can turn a deaf ear to my words.

17:43.240 --> 17:44.310
Does Boss He know

17:45.640 --> 17:46.770
you're doing this??

17:51.000 --> 17:51.550
Dahua.

17:52.590 --> 17:54.190
You stay here and watch them.

17:54.920 --> 17:56.140
Don't let them kill each other.

17:56.140 --> 17:56.610
Okay.

17:57.200 --> 17:57.830
Cheng,

17:57.920 --> 17:58.810
why are you leaving?

17:58.810 --> 17:59.960
Cheng, don't go.

18:00.350 --> 18:01.680
Save me, Cheng!

18:02.030 --> 18:02.430
Cheng.

18:02.940 --> 18:05.000
How did you know he was selling powder?

18:05.000 --> 18:05.720
Help!

18:27.030 --> 18:27.690
That's him.

18:32.150 --> 18:33.680
Print out his frontal face.

18:33.680 --> 18:35.210
Print out a few more angles.

18:42.550 --> 18:43.270
Senior.

18:44.160 --> 18:45.590
You asked me to investigate that car.

18:45.590 --> 18:46.240
I found the owner

18:46.240 --> 18:47.200
and got the dashcam.

18:47.200 --> 18:48.480
It actually captured the guy's
frontal face.

18:48.480 --> 18:49.200
Have you confirmed his identity?

18:49.200 --> 18:49.830
Yes.

18:49.830 --> 18:50.480
It's the killer

18:50.480 --> 18:51.960
in a serial murder case in Huaiguang City
20 years ago

18:51.960 --> 18:52.690
named Qi Yan.

18:53.070 --> 18:53.550
Who?

18:54.440 --> 18:55.070
Qi Yan.

18:59.550 --> 19:00.400
Qi Yan!

19:14.680 --> 19:15.810
This is impossible.

19:16.550 --> 19:18.960
This is the killer of the
Huaiguang serial murder case.

19:18.960 --> 19:20.920
This case was originally an unsolved case.

19:20.920 --> 19:22.830
I handled it myself 20 years ago.

19:22.940 --> 19:23.480
The 8.17 Case

19:23.480 --> 19:25.010
brought this case up again.

19:25.240 --> 19:26.040
It was closed.

19:26.510 --> 19:28.000
Yao Weihai took his men to the scene

19:28.000 --> 19:29.260
and caught the killer.

19:29.510 --> 19:30.750
You mean him?

19:31.350 --> 19:32.350
His name is Qi Yan.

19:32.550 --> 19:34.090
He resisted arrest at the scene.

19:34.090 --> 19:36.300
The police shot him to death on the spot.

19:36.720 --> 19:37.880
He's dead?

19:38.130 --> 19:39.140
Dead!

19:39.170 --> 19:40.760
Dead as a doornail!

19:41.310 --> 19:42.440
Where is Yao Weihai?

19:43.070 --> 19:44.270
He went to the Provincial Bureau.

19:44.270 --> 19:45.530
Could you be mistaken?

19:45.680 --> 19:46.720
No!

19:46.960 --> 19:48.200
Even if he turned to ashes,

19:48.200 --> 19:50.260
I could still smell the stench on him.

19:50.620 --> 19:52.220
Throughout the whole crime,

19:52.790 --> 19:54.920
he deliberately avoided the cameras.

19:55.070 --> 19:55.830
How could he appear

19:55.830 --> 19:57.310
in the dashcam?

19:57.790 --> 19:59.250
Was it really by accident?

19:59.580 --> 20:00.450
Or

20:00.610 --> 20:02.740
did he deliberately let us see his face

20:02.860 --> 20:04.600
and remind us of Qi Yan?

20:05.920 --> 20:07.780
Has the video been tampered with?

20:08.160 --> 20:08.880
No.

20:09.440 --> 20:10.470
There's no issue with it.

20:10.470 --> 20:12.130
The forensic results are out.

20:16.380 --> 20:18.680
The semen stain we extracted
from the deceased

20:18.680 --> 20:20.270
was compared with the DNA database.

20:20.270 --> 20:21.130
It is confirmed

20:21.590 --> 20:22.640
to be Qi Yan's.

20:35.350 --> 20:36.810
I want to talk to my student

20:37.550 --> 20:38.510
privately.

20:38.730 --> 20:39.380
Okay.

20:39.410 --> 20:41.210
Come, let's analyze it outside.

20:41.270 --> 20:42.270
Don't worry.

20:42.440 --> 20:43.030
Come.

20:43.030 --> 20:43.630
Come here.

20:58.110 --> 20:58.960
It's okay.

21:02.200 --> 21:03.200
I'll go out first.

21:17.440 --> 21:18.510
Dead?

21:18.750 --> 21:20.400
And they saw it with their own eyes?

21:20.400 --> 21:21.400
How do we investigate that?

21:21.400 --> 21:23.030
How can we catch a dead man?

21:24.350 --> 21:25.260
About this video,

21:25.260 --> 21:27.480
whether it's intentional or unintentional,

21:27.480 --> 21:29.340
we can't let it lead us by the nose.

21:29.920 --> 21:31.030
We will investigate

21:31.030 --> 21:31.920
as we should.

21:33.880 --> 21:34.830
You're right.

21:49.480 --> 21:52.030
Do you remember what I told you before?

21:53.440 --> 21:56.310
If one path is a dead end,

21:57.000 --> 21:58.060
what should you do?

21:59.550 --> 22:00.550
Try another path.

22:02.000 --> 22:03.530
Things that seem

22:05.160 --> 22:06.480
impossible now

22:08.000 --> 22:09.790
will all make sense

22:10.440 --> 22:12.520
when the real killer is caught.

22:14.330 --> 22:16.050
Didn't I tell you before?

22:16.200 --> 22:17.330
This Qi Yan

22:18.070 --> 22:19.310
was targeting you.

22:19.870 --> 22:22.230
Why did he show his face on the monitor?

22:22.310 --> 22:23.840
And showing only half of it?

22:24.630 --> 22:26.760
He's throwing down a challenge to you.

22:28.640 --> 22:30.040
But at least I can confirm

22:30.720 --> 22:33.580
that this person is definitely
connected to Qi Yan.

22:35.110 --> 22:35.960
I...

22:36.920 --> 22:38.750
I want to go back to Huaiguang

22:39.590 --> 22:41.030
to investigate

22:41.750 --> 22:42.920
Qi Yan's case again.

22:43.510 --> 22:44.830
See if I can

22:45.030 --> 22:47.350
find any new clues.

22:50.240 --> 22:50.830
Okay.

22:55.680 --> 22:56.790
Just like that,

22:56.960 --> 22:59.240
we're back to where we were 5 years ago.

23:00.960 --> 23:02.720
This Qi Yan...

23:02.750 --> 23:03.850
He erased his entire life history.

23:03.850 --> 23:05.850
He's completely clean now

23:06.310 --> 23:09.270
as if he just appeared out of thin air.

23:10.270 --> 23:11.480
The matter Yao Weihai

23:11.880 --> 23:13.160
didn't figure out back then

23:13.160 --> 23:14.820
is still very difficult for us

23:16.310 --> 23:17.720
to investigate now.

23:19.720 --> 23:20.350
But

23:21.030 --> 23:23.560
we must investigate,
no matter how hard it is.

23:35.200 --> 23:36.880
Book me a train ticket

23:37.200 --> 23:37.960
for today

23:37.990 --> 23:38.790
to Huaiguang.

23:40.110 --> 23:40.550
Right.

23:41.920 --> 23:42.350
Right.

23:42.590 --> 23:44.590
Send me the details after you buy it.

23:45.510 --> 23:47.480
Grandpa, are you back?

23:49.340 --> 23:50.600
My little sweetheart.

23:52.410 --> 23:53.440
I'm not back there.

23:53.440 --> 23:54.720
I'm working.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.000
Grandpa,

23:56.000 --> 23:58.790
can I keep a duckling?

23:59.190 --> 24:00.030
Of course.

24:00.270 --> 24:01.720
You can buy as many as you want.

24:01.720 --> 24:03.200
Mom won't let me.

24:03.400 --> 24:05.750
She said ducklings poop everywhere.

24:06.110 --> 24:07.480
All ducklings poop.

24:07.480 --> 24:09.200
The ones that don't poop are toys.

24:09.200 --> 24:10.750
I will buy them for you when I get back.

24:10.750 --> 24:11.750
I'll buy a whole basket of them for you.

24:11.750 --> 24:13.880
Grandpa, sing me a song.

24:13.880 --> 24:14.590
No singing.

24:14.790 --> 24:15.510
Please sing!

24:15.510 --> 24:16.110
Okay, okay.

24:16.110 --> 24:17.150
I'll sing.

24:20.070 --> 24:22.590
♪ Under the bridge at the door ♪

24:22.790 --> 24:25.110
♪ A bunch of ducks came ♪

24:25.200 --> 24:27.350
♪ Come and count them ♪

24:27.590 --> 24:29.200
♪ Two, four, six, seven, eight ♪

24:40.640 --> 24:42.830
♪ Come and count them ♪

24:43.000 --> 24:44.640
♪ Two, four, six, seven, eight ♪

24:45.510 --> 24:46.160
No more singing.

24:46.160 --> 24:47.420
I still have work to do.

24:47.960 --> 24:49.070
Goodbye, Grandpa.

24:49.190 --> 24:49.830
Goodbye.

24:49.930 --> 24:51.590
Dad, you can't spoil her like this.

24:51.590 --> 24:53.400
Stop nagging!

24:54.270 --> 24:56.270
Hurry up and buy me the train ticket!

25:00.110 --> 25:00.750
Prof.

25:01.680 --> 25:02.550
No rush.

25:02.890 --> 25:03.890
Go back tomorrow.

25:06.000 --> 25:07.550
Whenever I think of this Qi Yan,

25:07.550 --> 25:08.750
I feel so suffocated.

25:09.120 --> 25:10.470
The sooner it's resolved,

25:10.470 --> 25:12.070
the sooner I'll feel at ease.

25:14.640 --> 25:16.190
This piece of garbage

25:19.820 --> 25:21.650
ruined my best student.

25:27.960 --> 25:28.530
Prof,

25:31.200 --> 25:32.920
did I disappoint you again?

25:33.400 --> 25:34.070
No.

25:35.070 --> 25:36.940
You've never disappointed me.

25:38.240 --> 25:38.850
Really.

25:39.980 --> 25:42.220
You've never disappointed me.

25:47.220 --> 25:48.110
Never.

26:01.790 --> 26:02.440
Hansheng,

26:07.050 --> 26:08.780
you've never disappointed me.

26:09.310 --> 26:10.590
You used to be

26:11.510 --> 26:14.230
a cold machine.

26:15.510 --> 26:16.550
But now,

26:17.530 --> 26:20.090
you're a living human being,

26:21.270 --> 26:22.160
you know?

26:23.270 --> 26:24.440
Now you have

26:24.460 --> 26:25.790
emotions and desires.

26:38.120 --> 26:39.030
Tell me,

26:39.680 --> 26:41.230
are you and Zhou

26:41.250 --> 26:42.940
going to have a belated wedding ceremony?

26:42.940 --> 26:44.900
I'm busy with work this year.

26:45.330 --> 26:46.440
Hurry up.

26:46.470 --> 26:48.510
I'm waiting to hold your baby.

26:50.600 --> 26:51.310
I'm telling you...

26:51.310 --> 26:51.970
It will be soon.

26:51.970 --> 26:53.830
I even thought of their nickname.

26:54.960 --> 26:56.200
If it's a boy,

26:56.480 --> 26:57.920
we'll call him Little Pickle.

26:57.920 --> 26:58.840
Little Pickle?

26:58.870 --> 26:59.430
Yes.

26:59.450 --> 27:00.680
If it's a girl,

27:00.700 --> 27:02.390
we'll call her Rice Porridge.

27:03.040 --> 27:03.970
Isn't it nice?

27:05.520 --> 27:07.320
I have to ask Zhou Jin about this.

27:08.790 --> 27:09.650
Director Wang,

27:10.030 --> 27:11.000
when you arrive in Huaiguang,

27:11.000 --> 27:13.920
just contact Zhou if you need anything.

27:14.320 --> 27:14.850
Okay.

27:16.230 --> 27:17.890
I'll go straight to the hotel.

27:17.920 --> 27:18.980
I'll grab my things

27:19.720 --> 27:20.680
and head to the train station.

27:20.680 --> 27:21.550
No need to see me out.

27:21.550 --> 27:23.150
Thank you for your hard work.

27:23.920 --> 27:24.760
Mr. Wang,

27:24.790 --> 27:25.720
let me drive you.

27:26.450 --> 27:27.840
Let me do it, Prof.

27:28.550 --> 27:30.080
Are you worried, unhappy, .

27:30.960 --> 27:32.430
or just unwilling

27:32.430 --> 27:34.090
that Zhou is going to drive me?

27:34.140 --> 27:34.820
Exactly.

27:35.160 --> 27:36.090
Give me the keys.

27:40.500 --> 27:41.530
Wait for me a moment, Mr. Wang.

27:41.530 --> 27:42.620
I'm going to change clothes.

27:42.620 --> 27:43.590
Okay, hurry up.

27:55.090 --> 27:56.050
Zhou.

27:56.890 --> 27:59.030
You've been working for a few years,
right?

27:59.030 --> 28:00.990
I graduated from Jingzhou Police Academy.

28:00.990 --> 28:01.940
After graduation,

28:01.940 --> 28:04.200
I worked at a grassroots police station.

28:04.330 --> 28:06.820
Then I was transferred to
the Public Security Brigade.

28:06.820 --> 28:07.740
A year ago,

28:08.110 --> 28:10.480
I just came to
the Criminal Investigation Brigade.

28:10.480 --> 28:11.410
That's not easy.

28:15.070 --> 28:15.920
Mr. Wang.

28:17.070 --> 28:18.680
About the Huaiguang
serial murder case,

28:18.680 --> 28:20.900
is it true that apart from the task force,

28:20.900 --> 28:22.250
even police officers

28:22.590 --> 28:23.590
are not authorized to know

28:23.590 --> 28:25.190
more details about the case?

28:25.210 --> 28:27.210
This case was closed a long time ago.

28:28.130 --> 28:29.210
In principle,

28:30.130 --> 28:33.510
it's past the criminal investigation
confidentiality phase.

28:33.510 --> 28:35.510
It's not that we can't talk about it.

28:35.570 --> 28:37.640
But this case involves the 8.17 Case

28:38.450 --> 28:40.860
and the safety of the informant.

28:41.280 --> 28:43.140
That's why it wasn't made public.

28:43.920 --> 28:45.000
Was the informant

28:46.670 --> 28:47.600
Hansheng?

28:51.220 --> 28:52.420
He told you?

28:54.830 --> 28:57.660
Knowing is better than not.

28:59.230 --> 29:00.950
He just told me briefly.

29:02.000 --> 29:03.350
After all, there are many things

29:03.350 --> 29:05.010
he can't discuss externally.

29:05.980 --> 29:06.700
Mr. Wang.

29:08.960 --> 29:09.880
I want to know

29:10.260 --> 29:12.260
more details about these two cases.

29:14.230 --> 29:15.890
Because my brother Zhou Chuan

29:16.390 --> 29:19.920
was the special police officer
who sacrificed in the 8.17 Case.

29:21.430 --> 29:22.760
What do you want to know?

29:24.220 --> 29:25.310
I want to know...

29:26.890 --> 29:28.950
Besides what you said at the meeting,

29:29.030 --> 29:30.830
is there anything else special?

29:31.090 --> 29:32.160
For example,

29:33.120 --> 29:34.040
did Qi Yan

29:34.810 --> 29:36.140
show any special hatred

29:36.920 --> 29:37.750
towards the police

29:37.750 --> 29:39.440
in the Huaiguang Case?

29:41.900 --> 29:43.430
Hatred towards the police?

29:47.190 --> 29:47.990
My brother...

29:51.640 --> 29:52.970
His death was horrific.

29:57.800 --> 29:59.460
Of course he hated the police.

30:01.000 --> 30:01.810
Hansheng

30:04.410 --> 30:05.780
almost lost his life.

30:10.770 --> 30:11.830
Didn't he tell you?

30:15.160 --> 30:15.990
I didn't know.

30:18.520 --> 30:19.780
It's his personality.

30:28.510 --> 30:33.400
[2012]

30:54.400 --> 30:57.200
A large amount of drugs was injected
into the body.

30:57.240 --> 30:58.070
It takes time

30:58.990 --> 30:59.990
to clear them out.

31:52.300 --> 31:53.170
You're awake,

31:53.520 --> 31:54.590
Pup.

31:58.370 --> 31:59.410
Prof.

32:01.570 --> 32:03.220
Don't tell my dad.

32:04.750 --> 32:06.270
I don't want him to...

32:07.720 --> 32:09.720
I don't want him to...

32:20.010 --> 32:20.860
I'm here.

32:22.100 --> 32:22.960
I'm right here.

32:38.440 --> 32:39.680
The 8.17 Case

32:40.350 --> 32:41.480
made Jiang Hansheng

32:41.560 --> 32:43.510
change his career path.

32:45.660 --> 32:46.900
And he almost

32:47.170 --> 32:49.030
lost his life to Qi Yan.

32:51.720 --> 32:53.580
You didn't know all this, did you?

32:55.510 --> 32:56.160
Red light!

33:01.430 --> 33:02.430
Back then,

33:02.450 --> 33:04.310
that Chen Li, who turned himself in,

33:04.310 --> 33:05.510
was just a scapegoat.

33:06.110 --> 33:07.350
The true killer

33:07.680 --> 33:10.250
of the Huaiguang serial murder case
20 years ago

33:10.250 --> 33:11.320
is still out there.

33:11.430 --> 33:13.290
But reopening the investigation

33:14.200 --> 33:15.530
would be too difficult.

33:20.560 --> 33:22.090
Even when it was 5 years ago,

33:22.720 --> 33:24.650
it had been 15 years since the case.

33:25.440 --> 33:27.830
The backbone of the investigation team
back then was transferred,

33:27.830 --> 33:29.200
retired,

33:30.160 --> 33:32.640
or even died in other cases.

33:30.540 --> 33:35.410
[2012]

33:33.790 --> 33:36.510
The Huaiguang serial murder case
is significant.

33:36.510 --> 33:37.750
Chen Li confessed,

33:37.850 --> 33:38.850
but then he died.

33:39.200 --> 33:40.400
There was no proof.

33:41.030 --> 33:42.480
Without solid,

33:42.480 --> 33:43.750
convincing evidence,

33:44.160 --> 33:46.920
we couldn't reopen it based on
enthusiasm alone.

33:47.720 --> 33:50.790
We must be absolutely determined
to find the truth.

33:50.880 --> 33:52.410
If the investigation fails

33:52.440 --> 33:53.790
and it only affects me,

33:53.850 --> 33:55.040
it's no big deal.

33:55.510 --> 33:58.590
But what about the many police officers
in the Crime Research Lab?

33:58.590 --> 34:00.120
Before having a sure grasp,

34:00.900 --> 34:02.710
I really have too many concerns.

34:08.190 --> 34:08.710
Come in.

34:10.550 --> 34:11.110
Prof.

34:11.920 --> 34:13.400
The comparison results are in.

34:13.400 --> 34:14.960
The criminal's DNA

34:14.960 --> 34:16.030
extracted from Zhou Chuan's clothes

34:16.030 --> 34:17.960
matches perfectly with the DNA

34:17.960 --> 34:18.960
from the 1997 Huaiguang Case.

34:18.960 --> 34:20.159
It's the same person.

34:20.480 --> 34:21.440
I'll submit an appeal

34:21.440 --> 34:23.840
to the provincial procuratorate
in my personal capacity

34:23.840 --> 34:26.770
to request a reinvestigation
of the Huaiguang Case.

34:27.120 --> 34:30.360
Hansheng insisted on participating in
the investigation.

34:30.360 --> 34:32.020
This kid is really something.

34:32.510 --> 34:33.670
First, he got

34:33.710 --> 34:35.480
the DNA comparison report,

34:36.190 --> 34:38.110
proving that the sexual assault suspect
in the Huaiguang Case

34:38.110 --> 34:40.960
was involved in the 8.17 Case.

34:41.510 --> 34:43.000
Then he found the forensic doctor

34:43.000 --> 34:44.960
who was in charge of the autopsy back then

34:44.960 --> 34:46.620
and persuaded him to testify,

34:47.190 --> 34:48.280
and got him to write

34:48.960 --> 34:50.440
such a thick appeal.

34:51.150 --> 34:52.550
Under great pressure,

34:53.070 --> 34:55.070
he finally submitted this material

34:55.070 --> 34:57.000
to the provincial procuratorate.

34:58.920 --> 35:00.440
It took a lot of trouble

35:00.960 --> 35:03.420
to get the case reopened
for investigation.

35:04.440 --> 35:05.600
The investigation back then

35:05.600 --> 35:07.260
wasn't as smooth as imagined.

35:07.960 --> 35:10.490
After all, 15 years had passed
after the case.

35:10.720 --> 35:13.070
Due to the technical limitations
in the 1990s,

35:13.070 --> 35:15.280
little evidence had remained.

35:16.320 --> 35:17.710
To find a criminal suspect

35:17.710 --> 35:19.510
among millions of people

35:19.710 --> 35:20.960
would require a lot of

35:21.230 --> 35:22.590
manpower and time.

35:22.880 --> 35:25.010
That was harder than reaching the sky.

35:25.320 --> 35:26.360
Hansheng

35:27.590 --> 35:29.320
decided not to wait any longer.

35:30.360 --> 35:31.880
He took a drastic measure.

35:33.630 --> 35:34.960
I want to ask you a favor.

35:35.510 --> 35:36.800
Contact a TV reporter

35:37.080 --> 35:38.150
and request an exclusive interview

35:38.150 --> 35:39.480
during prime time.

35:40.760 --> 35:41.690
Interview whom?

35:43.310 --> 35:44.710
Leader Yao will tell you.

35:51.980 --> 35:52.730
Senior.

35:52.760 --> 35:53.840
This is Yao Weihai.

35:54.070 --> 35:54.670
Well...

35:54.670 --> 35:56.510
did Jiang go to you?

35:56.840 --> 35:58.190
Jiang Hansheng is sitting in front of me.

35:58.190 --> 35:59.440
And you called me.

35:59.710 --> 36:01.210
He said you wanted to talk to me?

36:01.210 --> 36:01.510
Well...

36:01.510 --> 36:03.770
What are you two plotting behind my back?

36:03.940 --> 36:05.100
He came to me.

36:05.630 --> 36:06.630
The locals in Huaiguang

36:06.630 --> 36:08.630
weren't that cooperative
with his investigation.

36:08.630 --> 36:10.810
I don't have much progress here either.

36:10.810 --> 36:13.500
Since he said he has a way
to lure the real culprit out,

36:13.500 --> 36:14.960
I think we can give it a try.

36:15.260 --> 36:16.010
Look,

36:16.760 --> 36:18.070
how about lending Jiang

36:18.070 --> 36:18.840
to me?

36:18.920 --> 36:20.380
Don't even think about it!

36:20.400 --> 36:22.200
When the murder acted alone,

36:22.220 --> 36:23.620
he killed so many women.

36:24.030 --> 36:26.630
Now he has a complete organization
behind him,

36:26.720 --> 36:28.710
and he even dares to kill police officers.

36:28.710 --> 36:31.310
That murder has been at large
for over a decade.

36:31.320 --> 36:32.360
What are you thinking?

36:32.360 --> 36:33.030
At this critical moment,

36:33.030 --> 36:34.960
you want my student to risk his life
for you?

36:34.960 --> 36:35.510
Senior.

36:36.230 --> 36:37.150
Right now,

36:37.150 --> 36:38.710
I'll make a solemn pledge to you.

36:38.710 --> 36:39.400
Once he comes,

36:39.400 --> 36:41.400
I'll have him guarded 24/7,

36:41.630 --> 36:43.920
and absolutely guarantee his safety. Okay?

36:43.920 --> 36:44.710
Enough!

36:45.590 --> 36:46.280
Hold on!

36:48.220 --> 36:49.420
If I say I disagree,

36:51.070 --> 36:52.270
will you listen to me?

36:52.280 --> 36:52.760
No.

36:52.830 --> 36:53.800
You little brat!

36:53.800 --> 36:55.760
I knew you would answer me like this.

36:55.760 --> 36:57.820
You're just here to cause me trouble.

36:58.840 --> 36:59.300
Senior.

36:59.470 --> 37:00.630
Don't get so angry.

37:00.650 --> 37:01.840
Let's talk about it again.

37:01.840 --> 37:02.700
No need to talk.

37:04.800 --> 37:06.000
I will lend him to you.

37:07.000 --> 37:07.630
Yao.

37:08.280 --> 37:10.410
You know his weight in my research lab.

37:10.710 --> 37:12.710
I'm putting this kid in your hands.

37:12.880 --> 37:14.960
If anything happens to him,

37:15.630 --> 37:17.150
our 32-year friendship

37:17.280 --> 37:18.320
is over!

37:18.360 --> 37:19.160
Goodbye!

37:19.190 --> 37:19.840
That's it!

37:23.280 --> 37:24.280
Yao Weihai

37:24.570 --> 37:26.050
is now at Nancheng Branch.

37:27.030 --> 37:28.890
He doesn't have the face to see me.

37:29.590 --> 37:30.400
Maybe

37:30.590 --> 37:31.110
Leader Yao

37:31.110 --> 37:33.230
just wanted to solve the case
as soon as possible.

37:33.230 --> 37:34.960
In order to solve the case? Him?

37:36.440 --> 37:37.940
Yao Weihai has become obsessed

37:37.940 --> 37:39.380
ever since he became

37:40.000 --> 37:41.800
head of the investigation team.

37:42.760 --> 37:43.760
Whatever you say,

37:44.320 --> 37:46.650
if it weren't for his dereliction of duty,

37:47.360 --> 37:49.490
would Hansheng have suffered so much?

37:52.230 --> 37:52.880
Prof.

37:53.430 --> 37:54.690
I'll take tomorrow off

37:54.710 --> 37:55.400
to prepare a suit

37:55.400 --> 37:56.360
for the show.

37:57.320 --> 37:57.960
Go ahead.

37:58.670 --> 37:59.600
Then I'll go now.

38:01.360 --> 38:02.160
Wait a moment.

38:05.480 --> 38:06.960
Tell me more.

38:08.110 --> 38:10.960
Why do you want to do a legal show

38:11.150 --> 38:12.480
during prime time on TV?

38:14.190 --> 38:15.520
Here's the thing, Prof.

38:16.670 --> 38:18.490
The murder has long lacked affection,

38:18.490 --> 38:19.660
so he could have easily developed

38:19.660 --> 38:21.660
histrionic personality disorder.

38:22.190 --> 38:23.360
If I were him,

38:23.840 --> 38:25.710
I would definitely monitor the police's
movements

38:25.710 --> 38:27.570
through every possible channel.

38:28.000 --> 38:28.800
If necessary,

38:29.400 --> 38:31.530
I would even give a trivial statement.

38:31.960 --> 38:32.710
This way,

38:32.960 --> 38:34.510
I could observe up close

38:34.510 --> 38:36.800
those fools dancing to my tune.

38:43.960 --> 38:46.630
You want to challenge the killer

38:48.190 --> 38:49.920
on TV?

38:53.480 --> 38:54.800
Welcome, sir.

38:54.800 --> 38:56.400
Looking for a tailored suit?

38:56.760 --> 38:57.320
Yes.

38:57.510 --> 38:58.400
Take a look.

38:59.000 --> 39:00.260
What color do you like?

39:02.190 --> 39:02.880
Red.

39:04.360 --> 39:06.480
In medicine, there's a scale

39:06.480 --> 39:07.550
for psychopathy assessment,

39:07.550 --> 39:09.110
called the Hare Psychopathy Checklist.

39:09.110 --> 39:10.970
It includes 20 assessment items.

39:11.480 --> 39:12.110
For example,

39:12.110 --> 39:13.920
does the person appear charming?

39:13.920 --> 39:15.510
Are they highly manipulative?

39:15.510 --> 39:17.440
Is their emotional range limited?

39:17.710 --> 39:19.190
That's what we usually call

39:19.190 --> 39:20.150
lack of empathy.

39:21.150 --> 39:21.800
Also,

39:22.000 --> 39:23.670
grandiose sense of self-worth,

39:23.670 --> 39:25.440
pathological lying, and a series of

39:25.440 --> 39:26.970
other personality traits.

39:27.720 --> 39:28.810
I believe that

39:28.840 --> 39:30.510
if the killer
of the red dress serial murder case

39:30.510 --> 39:32.110
were to take this checklist,

39:32.110 --> 39:33.960
he would score high on many items.

39:33.960 --> 39:35.090
But there's one item

39:35.340 --> 39:36.440
that he would score low on.

39:36.440 --> 39:37.440
Which one?

39:38.510 --> 39:40.110
Limited emotional range.

39:40.880 --> 39:42.230
Because, on the contrary,

39:42.230 --> 39:43.690
his emotions are intense.

39:44.070 --> 39:45.000
Strong emotions

39:45.140 --> 39:45.800
are what drove him to kill

39:45.800 --> 39:47.650
and stage the crime scenes.

39:48.280 --> 39:50.800
From how meticulously
he planned and executed the murders,

39:50.800 --> 39:52.320
he appears to be calm

39:52.340 --> 39:53.400
and cold-blooded.

39:53.510 --> 39:55.570
But the drive behind his violent acts

39:55.920 --> 39:57.510
comes from stimulation.

39:57.880 --> 39:59.230
Because deep inside,

39:59.550 --> 40:01.880
he's still a child with emotional trauma.

40:12.030 --> 40:13.240
Hansheng knew

40:13.490 --> 40:15.490
the murder's psychological flaws.

40:16.150 --> 40:17.400
He knew what to say

40:17.400 --> 40:18.590
to provoke him.

40:19.400 --> 40:20.550
His method

40:20.710 --> 40:22.550
worked very quickly.

40:25.480 --> 40:26.540
They took the bait.

40:28.720 --> 40:30.050
Keep a close eye on them.

40:39.670 --> 40:40.330
Don't move.

40:41.460 --> 40:42.790
Move and I'll shoot you.

40:45.880 --> 40:46.590
Let me go!

40:47.150 --> 40:47.880
Let me go!

40:51.930 --> 40:52.810
Command center,

40:52.810 --> 40:54.280
Jiang Hansheng was forced into a car.

40:54.280 --> 40:55.430
It's a black Hyundai.

40:55.430 --> 40:56.690
We're following them.

40:57.580 --> 40:58.710
Jiang Hansheng said

40:59.100 --> 41:00.190
serial killers

41:00.210 --> 41:02.010
look at their prey differently.

41:02.150 --> 41:03.680
He can tell the difference.

41:15.260 --> 41:16.380
Tie his hands.

41:24.800 --> 41:25.510
Tie him up.

41:30.710 --> 41:31.840
Who sent you?

41:32.860 --> 41:34.370
Our target isn't in the car.

41:34.370 --> 41:36.170
Keep following via the tracker.

41:43.330 --> 41:44.190
Officer Jiang.

41:44.870 --> 41:46.270
You've never even met me.

41:46.660 --> 41:49.460
How can you be so confident
that you understand me?

42:40.150 --> 42:40.950
Stop!

42:43.120 --> 42:44.520
Stop! Don't run!

42:50.670 --> 42:51.400
He's gone.

42:51.420 --> 42:52.480
We found his phone

42:52.480 --> 42:54.540
and the tracker on his boutonniere
in the car.

42:54.540 --> 42:55.200
What did you say?

42:55.200 --> 42:56.330
He's gone?

42:56.550 --> 42:58.110
How could he be gone?
